&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implementation of the software portion of MAC (Medium Access Control) and mobile ad-hoc networking routing protocols.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network management software and web interface implementation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implementation of different security protocols and encryption algorithms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Audio streaming and push-to-talk voice application implementation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze and improve product security and robustness to meet certain regulatory requirements such as NIST FIPS 140-3 and NIAP Common Criteria.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implementation of testing software for product performance and reliability testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Device driver and board support package development and maintenance for both ARM and RISC-V based systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Linux system customization and scripting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform other related duties of which the above are representative.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
